&lt;p&gt;Integrity Rehab Group is an industry leading therapy management company that partners with physician practices across the nation. In partnering with&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://suncoastorthopaedic.com/&quot;&gt;Suncoast Orthopaedic Institute&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;we have become a preferred outpatient orthopedic therapy service provider to the &lt;strong&gt;Venice, FL &lt;/strong&gt;community. To further support the needs of this community, we are looking to add a &lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Certified Occupational/Hand Therapy Assistant&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; to our team that is committed to providing a remarkable patient experience through advancing our vision of coordinating patient-centered care with an emphasis on comprehensive evidence-based treatment. This is enhanced through building integral relationships with our physician partners. Together, we strive to provide exceptional patient outcomes and a positive atmosphere for patient healing while promoting a collaborative and supportive work environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hourly Rate: $30-35&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
