&lt;li&gt;Customer Service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create an inviting clinic atmosphere.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make all welcome calls
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and influence arrival rate through creation of a great customer experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
